Reverse Number :-
        To reverse a number, you basically flip its digits from back to front.


algorithm:-

Step 1:-
Start
Step 2:-
Initialize variables
num → original number
rev = 0
Step 3:-
Repeat while num > 0
Find last digit
digit = num % 10
Add digit to reverse number
rev = rev * 10 + digit
Remove last digit from original number
num = num // 10
Step 4:-
Display rev
Step 5:-
Stop







